==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Candle meter
<hw>Candle meter</hw>. <fld>(Photom.)</fld> <def>The illumination given
by a standard candle at a distance of one meter; -- used as a unit of
illumination, except in Great Britain.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Candlenut</ent>⟦br⟧
